sources.description:
Behind The Line: Escape to Dunkirk - A POW is singled out by a Nazi Commander, for his boxing abilities. He wants to humiliate him against his own champion. The POW's use the upcoming fight as a diversion for a mass breakout to try and get as many soldiers back to Dunkirk and freedom.
2020.  Stars: Joel Phillimore, James Haynes, Chris Simmons
